1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://crustbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bikes Sea Monster Bombora</a></h3>\n<p>Cheech, the co-owner of Crust Bikes and partner of Matt, named the latest Bombora model the â€œSea Monster,â€ inspired by how grumpy Matt gets when there are no waves to surf. The Bombora needs no introduction here but the paint job and graphics, designed by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/azaazelus\" target=\"_blank\">Gaetan Sahsah</a> deserve a special, in-depth look.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-06.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-03.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-04.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/CrustBikes_SeaMonsterBombora-05.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The entire frame is covered in an iridescent glow, beautifully replicated the caustic reflection on the ocean floor.</p>\n<p>These will be available today at <a href=\"https://crustbikes.com/collections/frames\" target=\"_blank\">Crust Bikes</a>, Matt and Cheechâ€™s new bike shop in Australia, <a href=\"https://www.heapsgoodgarage.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">Heaps Good Garage</a>, <a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Lug</a>, and <a href=\"https://shop.circles-jp.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">Circles</a> in Japan.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1179\" height=\"1560\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?w=1179&amp;quality=75 1179w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?resize=1024,1355&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?resize=768,1016&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?resize=700,926&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3586.jpg?resize=1161,1536&amp;quality=75 1161w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"976\" height=\"1295\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3570.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3570.jpg?w=976&amp;quality=75 976w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3570.jpg?resize=768,1019&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3570.jpg?resize=700,929&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1059\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3572.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3572.jpg?w=1059&amp;quality=75 1059w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3572.jpg?resize=1024,1238&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3572.jpg?resize=768,928&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/IMG_3572.jpg?resize=700,846&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://meriwethercycles.com/product/stem-stash/\" target=\"_blank\">Meriwether Cycles Stemstash</a> $125/135</h3>\n<p>420 breaks on the trail or at camp after a long day of riding can be the perfect ticket to a nice, solid night of sleep. There are no shortage of stash pipes and one-hitters on the market but the Meriwether Stemstash adds a few clever details to this high-hardware.</p>\n<p>Machined in Northern California by Huston Precision out of 6061 aluminum (bowl) and stainless steel (stem), it has a secret storage compartment under the top-cap, accessible by a 4mm allen key or thumbscrew. The Stemstash fits inside your forkâ€™s steerer tube replacing the stock headset cap. It screws into the star nut, or an expansion plug*, and can be used to preload your headset, hide your stash, and never forget your safety break materials.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://meriwethercycles.com/product/stem-stash/\" target=\"_blank\">Meriwether Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-DarkOrange-Nov23-1_44de18b.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-DarkOrange-Nov23-1_44de18b.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-DarkOrange-Nov23-1_44de18b.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-DarkOrange-Nov23-1_44de18b.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-DarkOrange-Nov23-1_44de18b.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-Green-Nov23-1_d49f18c6-d19.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-Green-Nov23-1_d49f18c6-d19.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-Green-Nov23-1_d49f18c6-d19.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-Green-Nov23-1_d49f18c6-d19.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/ClemL-Green-Nov23-1_d49f18c6-d19.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/clem-frameset-winter-2023-presale-11-27-at-noon-pacific\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell Clem Smith Pre-Order</a> $1,300 (frameset)</h3>\n<p>Clem Smith Jr. is Rivendellâ€™s fat-tire, easy to fender &amp; rack, joyously upright and stable, and more affordable than the rest of our lineup bicycle frame.</p>\n<p>Theyâ€™re more affordable only because most of the joints are tig-welded instead of lugged. Tigs cut the construction time for each frame down by a lot so the price gets lower. Itâ€™s a perfectly strong way to make a bicycle, although not as pretty to look at as lugs.</p>\n<p>Clems still have a strong wide fork crown, napkin-ring reinforcement lugs at the headtube, and a beautiful well-designed seatlug, so it looks far from a generic bike.</p>\n<p>The pre-sale goes up today at NOON PST. See more at <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/products/clem-frameset-winter-2023-presale-11-27-at-noon-pacific\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1365\" height=\"2048\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?w=1365&amp;quality=75 1365w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?resize=1024,1536&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?resize=768,1152&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?resize=1335,2003&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6095-2_24bcf7b6-570a-4dad-bc.jpg?resize=700,1050&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/DSCF6138_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://ronsbikes.com/products/fabs-waxed-muscle-musette-coming-next-week\" target=\"_blank\">Fabioâ€™s Performance Purse Goldilocks</a> $55</h3>\n<p>Hey Josh, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/modern-musettes-handmade-sling-bags-roundup-review/\" target=\"_blank\">we got another musette</a> to add to your collection! These fun and handy Fabioâ€™s Performance Purses are made from 8.25 oz waxed canvas and pack down to the size of a softball.</p>\n<p>The perfect size for a city cruise to your local record shop at 13â€³ wide X 14â€³ tall the Fabâ€™s Purse will fit a large laptop and a few LP records; an ironic combo indeed. The inner pocket can hold your phone, wallet, multitool, and keys on a long elastic key hook and the closures are genuine velcro dots. Simple, packable, durable and effective.</p>\n<p>Right now the Goldilocks color is available but the Olive Fabâ€™s Purses sold out too fast the last time! See more at <a href=\"https://ronsbikes.com/products/fabs-waxed-muscle-musette-coming-next-week\" target=\"_blank\">Ronâ€™s Bikes</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2232\" height=\"1256\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?w=2232&amp;quality=75 2232w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=1024,576&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=2000,1125&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=768,432&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=1800,1013&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=1335,751&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=700,394&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=1536,864&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/chromag-riza-stem-group_1600x160.jpg?resize=2048,1152&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://us.chromagbikes.com/collections/stems/products/stems-riza\" target=\"_blank\">Chromag Riza Stem</a> $135</h3>\n<p>Chromag has used its knowledge of making stems for almost 20 years to create a new, highest level, Canadian-made bar grabber, perfect for a Darco, Doctahawk, or rowdy hardtail of your own!</p>\n<p>Thereâ€™s no doubt the RIZA is Chromagâ€™s finest stem to date. CNC machined in Whistler, Canada from premium 6061 billet aluminum, it features Chromagâ€™s new faded edge on the clamp face to help avoid hot spots and stress risers when your bar flexes under load.</p>\n<p>Also it looks really flippinâ€™ nice.</p>\n<p>The RIZA comes in a variety of colors, 31.8 and 35mm clamps and 32, 38 and 45mm lengths.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://us.chromagbikes.com/collections/stems/products/stems-riza\" target=\"_blank\">Chromag</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-21.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1276\" height=\"850\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-552.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-552.jpg?w=1276&amp;quality=75 1276w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-552.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-552.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/KNIVES_-552.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.horsebrand.co/goods/pack-knfe-anything-sheath\" target=\"_blank\">Horse Cycles Pack Knife with Water Bottle Boss Sheath</a> $120</h3>\n<p>The Horse Cycles Pack Knife is an incredibly versatile and sharp knife, perfect for camping and touring. Use it as a bush knife, to cook with, and even as a fillet knife for bikefishing trips. The weight of these knives in your hand is incredibly balanced and lightweight. Use it with a flint for starting a small campfire!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=1800,1201&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/11/NovemberCamping23-40.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Thomas from Horse just upped the ante with these Pack Knives with a custom sheath for mounting to any water bottle or cargo cage location. Mount under your water bottle cages or any other accessories or all on its own.</p>\n<p>The blade is made of AEBL 59 RC stainless 